lipidemia, acne, and venous thrombosis.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/97869/', '', 'Megestrol acetate, Ulipristal, Estetrol', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Velpatasvir, Rilpivirine, More', 1767369485);
